        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>International Nuclear Energy Financing Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the U.S. Executive Director at the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development (and the U.S. Executive Director at any other international financial institution deemed appropriate) to support financial assistance for the generation and distribution of nuclear energy, consistent with U.S. national security interests.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
